《[[同妻俱樂部|同妻俱樂部]]》（{{lang-en|''Grace and Frankie''}}）是一部於2015年5月8日在[[Netflix|Netflix]]首播的美國電視喜劇。<ref name="seriesorder">{{cite web|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2014/03/19/jane-fonda-and-lily-tomlin-back-together-again-in-grace-and-frankie-a-new-original-comedy-series-on-netflix-580503/20140319netflix01/|title=Jane Fonda and Lily Tomlin Back Together Again in "Grace and Frankie," A New Original Comedy Series on Netflix|publisher=[[富頓評論家|富頓評論家]]|date=2014-03-19|accessdate=2014-08-30}}</ref>本劇由{{link-en|瑪塔·考夫曼|Marta Kauffman}}與霍華德·J·莫里斯開創，並由[[珍·芳達|珍·芳達]]與[[莉莉·湯姆琳|莉莉·湯姆琳]]主演。

2015年5月26日，Netflix宣布續訂第二季。<ref name="season2">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/05/grace-and-frankie-renewed-season-2-netflix-1201433210/|title=‘Grace And Frankie’ Renewed For Season 2 By Netflix|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2015-05-26|accessdate=2015-05-19|archive-date=2018-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180826071435/https://deadline.com/2015/05/grace-and-frankie-renewed-season-2-netflix-1201433210/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年12月10日，在第二季尚未首播前，Netflix便宣布續訂第三季。<ref name="season3">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/grace-frankie-renewed-season-3-847685|title=Netflix Renews 'Grace and Frankie' for Third Season|publisher=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]|date=2015-12-10|accessdate=2015-12-10|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126074650/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/grace-frankie-renewed-season-3-847685|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年3月23日，在第3季即將開播、Netflix尚未續訂前，主創考夫曼透露已展開第4季的製作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/03/grace-frankie-season-3-spoilers-marta-kauffman-interview-jane-fonda-lily-tomlin-netflix-1202049413/|title=‘Grace And Frankie’: Marta Kauffman On Season 3, Dolly Parton & Why It’s Great To Be A Woman|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|author=Dominic Patten|date=2017-03-23|accessdate=2017-03-24|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223061923/https://deadline.com/2017/03/grace-frankie-season-3-spoilers-marta-kauffman-interview-jane-fonda-lily-tomlin-netflix-1202049413/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年4月12日，Netflix正式宣布續訂第4季。<ref name="Season 4 Renew">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2017/tv/news/grace-and-frankie-renewed-season-4-netflix-lisa-kudrow-1202028787/|title=‘Grace and Frankie’ Renewed for Season 4 at Netflix, Adds Lisa Kudrow|author=Joe Otterson|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]|date=2017-04-12|access-date=2017-04-13|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112011112/https://variety.com/2017/tv/news/grace-and-frankie-renewed-season-4-netflix-lisa-kudrow-1202028787/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年2月14日，Netflix正式宣布續訂第5季，全新一季也已展開製作一週多的時間。<ref name="Season 5 Renew Deadline">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2018/02/grace-and-frankie-renewed-season-5-rupaul-jane-fonda-lily-tomlin-netflix-1202288438/|title=‘Grace And Frankie’ Renewed For Season 5 On Netflix; RuPaul To Guest Star|author=Erik Pedersen|work=Deadline.com|date=2018-02-14|accessdate=2018-02-14|archive-date=2018-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180215192956/http://deadline.com/2018/02/grace-and-frankie-renewed-season-5-rupaul-jane-fonda-lily-tomlin-netflix-1202288438/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

